                                <note>
                                    <p> Notable feasts:</p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="3r" to="3r" scheme="folios"/>: St Canute (7 Jan.) </p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="6v" to="6v" scheme="folios"/>: St Hallvard (15 May, later addition) </p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="7v" to="7v" scheme="folios"/>: St William of Æbelholt (16 June); St Botolph (17 June) </p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="8v" to="8v" scheme="folios"/>: St Birgitta (23 July, later addition); St Olaf (29 July) </p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="10v" to="10v" scheme="folios"/>: St Birgitta (7 October, later addition) </p>
                                    <p/>
